<h1>Maxwell Covill</h1><img src="images/teachers/bio-pages/maxwell-covill.jpg" alt="Maxwell Covill" class="w350fr"><p>Maxwell found yoga 4 years ago as a physical practice to improve strength and flexibility, but soon discovered that it opened up infinite doors in terms of spirituality and how it allowed him to think and live differently.</p><p>With dedicated yoga practice he wishes to share and make the benefits accessible to all. Maxwell gained his Ashtanga Vinyasa teaching qualification in February 2015, while training at Kranti Yoga on Patnem Beach, Goa, India.</p>